---
import AppPageLayout from '../../../layouts/AppPageLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../../site.config';

const lastUpdated = 'May 17, 2026';
---

<AppPageLayout
  appName="Imposter"
  pageTitle="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the Imposter iOS game."
>
  <p class="muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

  <p>
    Imposter is a pass-and-play party game that runs entirely on your device. This privacy policy
    explains what information the app does and does not collect.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>None.</strong> Imposter does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information.
    The app has no user accounts, no servers, and makes no network requests.
  </p>

  <h2>Information You Enter</h2>
  <p>
    Player names and game settings you enter during play exist only in memory on your device
    for the duration of the game. They are not saved, synced, shared, or sent anywhere, and they
    are discarded when you close the app or start a new game.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics and Tracking</h2>
  <p>
    Imposter contains no analytics, no advertising, no third-party SDKs, and no tracking of any
    kind.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Because Imposter does not collect any information, it does not knowingly collect information
    from children under 13. The app is safe for use by players of any age.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted on this page with a new
    "Last updated" date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this privacy policy can be sent to
    <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>{siteConfig.email}</a>.
  </p>
</AppPageLayout>
